This time my LARGE order of nachos was mostly chips and crema and about one tablespoon of black beans on the bottom of all that. While the nachos are fresh, they lack consistency especially after the pandemic started.  If you order in person, make cure to check your nachos before leaving. I would not recommend ordering delivery as they can easily skimp on stuff without you knowing until it’s too late.  Edit: ingredients list also includes tomatoes and they gave me none
